{"type": "article", "id": 21799, "title": "Footmen lamp by Fotogen", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-03T08:14:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 70, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702110817ycoQ7kYT9SuO6fFA.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一盏无线灯，也是一款智能灯。拥有蓝牙控制，触摸式开关灯，可调光线，定时闹钟和受信息指示等多个功能。灯体是圆柱形的，使照射面积最大化，外圈是铝制的底座加细框，框子也可用做手提杆，有种提着灯笼的感觉，很灵活。电池充满后可最多支撑 5 个小时，适合需要夜读的学生。俄罗斯的设计师 St. Petersburg 设计了这款灯，2 月即将上市，<a href=\"http://www.fotogen.xyz/#crowd\">这里是购买链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110815og4urRbmtXqk9TZO.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110815GtMD850wuA34UH6F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64095238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110816sKlVJN4pH3uOc0Qm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110816rVoS4YW5XwU1KP3h.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6647619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <br>\r\n</figure><p></p>\n\n"}